txt.en: In the aftermath of the Sea-stone Mutiny, Umbar Baharbêl has been freed from the Heirs of Castamir and their rulers in the Empire of Ordâkh. Under the governance of the Kindred of the Coins, a council of seven chosen by the citizens of Umbar Baharbêl, the City of the Corsairs struggles to be reborn as a Free City—with tidings of hope and treachery found in equal measure as its people step out from the darkness that was cast upon them long ago by the Dark Lord, Sauron.
You have thoroughly explored Umbar Baharbêl, the City of the Corsairs.
You have completed many quests in Umbar Baharbêl, the City of the Corsairs.

In the aftermath of the Sea-stone Mutiny, Umbar Baharbêl has been freed from the Heirs of Castamir and their rulers in the Empire of Ordâkh. Under the governance of the Kindred of the Coins, a council of seven chosen by the citizens of Umbar Baharbêl, the City of the Corsairs struggles to be reborn as a Free City—with tidings of hope and treachery found in equal measure as its people step out from the darkness that was cast upon them long ago by the Dark Lord, Sauron.
